Job Description
*	12 -- 18 years of experience in the industry*	In depth expertise in one or two domains, with familiarity in at least one more domain.	e.g. Financials & Projects, with familiarity in SCM; SCM & Manufacturing, with familiarity in EAM / CRM, etc.	Has been hands-on in delivery of large, complex, global engagements 	Strong expertise in at least one product stack, with familiarity in at least one more	Exhibits a consulting flair / strong market-facing qualities 	Develop roadmaps, program plans, execute health checks & due diligence, make recommendations, etc.	Depth of expertise to engage with CxOs and develop customer relationships and earn their trust	Deep experience in one or two verticals	Self-driven, motivated, brings value to every interaction	Willing to get hands-on, to incubate engagements and be part of their governance	Should not be into project management / Program Management	Should not be into Practice development / Headcount / Revenue / Growth	Focus should entirely be in the domain (Financials, Supply Chain, HCM, etc.)	Ideally will be grounded and continue to remain hands-on on one product (EBS, PeopleSoft, etc.)	Exposure to additional platforms (SAP, Taleo, Successfactors, etc.) is a BIG plus. 	Should be able to develop a relationship with CxOs, senior business stakeholders, and engage as a thought leader in their space.
